case_circumstances:
On December 31, 1980, there was a fire at 3756 W. 25th St., Cleveland, OH.  This decedent was found in the rubble of that building on January 3, 1981 about 7:45 a.m. Numerous people from the building either leapt to their deaths or were incinerated by the fire.  
The fire was of undetermined origin.
